msg":"有隻叫百花蛇舌草煲嘅涼茶<br />\n好飲又好有效"},{"pid":"021ac2d9c0ef5c5eda310e2b48d4886e7d35975f","tid":406452,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T18:23:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢幾年生活習慣好差 想清下腸胃<br />\nbtw西梅汁好似對我無乜用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nM記啲奶茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n間中有飲 真係有料<br />\n但想用啲專用既產品清一次<br />\n利申排便正常"},{"pid":"d66b0a89b976a24462d6ad985dc626a259bb1328","tid":406452,"uid":59030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T18:48:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>奇亞籽 屙啲馳長瀨瀨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點食法最好"},{"pid":"d1b851a64de539796c1fbc08b8f5ea058dab91ee","tid":406452,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T18:54:10.000Z","msg":"最天然嘅飲品<br />\n檸檬溝鹽水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fc39053140132c810b23bef2ff5a00a2b5b284b","tid":406452,"uid":80294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T22:32:07.000Z","msg":"日日朝早搵啲鹽水灌腸"},{"pid":"47c289d3f90e667e7a331c21c806ea8ee380df94","tid":406452,"uid":83002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T23:18:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>奇亞籽 屙啲馳長瀨瀨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點食法最好</blockquote><br />\n我自己浸蜜糖水或者奶，或者屋企整甜品果陣加落去<br />\n平時痾粒粒屎，飲完就真係好似上面巴打講咁，痾條條屎，好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df03d467714fb50ec4b8980e80fe01c71972d64b","tid":406452,"uid":143173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T03:09:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>奇亞籽 屙啲馳長瀨瀨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點食法最好</blockquote><br />\n我自己浸蜜糖水或者奶，或者屋企整甜品果陣加落去<br />\n平時痾粒粒屎，飲完就真係好似上面巴打講咁，痾條條屎，好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係呀 豆漿都得<br />\n浸到佢發脹咗個口感幾得意 冇味"},{"pid":"f60821a924488342d16ff62cfe13cd197dbd94bb","tid":406452,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T03:39:20.000Z","msg":"我呢排都係朝早買冷壓果汁飲 <br />\n羽衣甘藍 青蘋果 啤梨 青瓜<br />\n呢隻對我最有用 又好飲 皮膚好左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但唔係清宿便 係保持定時有得痾 <br />\n<br />\n要清就用灌水法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上網有教"},{"pid":"130c625b248c4947c0a9cdecdd6fe0f395506ec6","tid":406452,"uid":116131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T03:44:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>奇亞籽 屙啲馳長瀨瀨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點食法最好</blockquote><br />\n我自己浸蜜糖水或者奶，或者屋企整甜品果陣加落去<br />\n平時痾粒粒屎，飲完就真係好似上面巴打講咁，痾條條屎，好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係呀 豆漿都得<br />\n浸到佢發脹咗個口感幾得意 冇味</blockquote><br />\n你地多數係邊到買？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n價錢又如何?"},{"pid":"919f4832ba06345bc9bc674263fda4d37e0b294a","tid":406452,"uid":121480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T03:46:09.000Z","msg":"地捫西梅乾 一次過食十粒左右"},{"pid":"79710d090c54bb552c9e9dda677d020d88188f49","tid":406452,"uid":11257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T03:46:51.000Z","msg":"譚仔"},{"pid":"d2e75fb48a2355691e9add56297640ab60cfa49a","tid":406452,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T03:48:33.000Z","msg":"慢零、屈神有隻乜乜奇異果汁，一盒有7包，畀你飲7日，沖嚟飲，飲親都痾到九彩，不過覺得買呢啲好貴，依家日日食奇異果＋運動好過"},{"pid":"d910c724b41a5ce19ff9a37340096e90b1500862","tid":406452,"uid":143173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T06:35:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockqu